data.value: select SP.Title,P.PlannerName,P.EmpCode,P.Position,D.Description As Department,M.EmpName,M.Position As PositionMem,M.Department As DepartmentMem , P.Description,P.TravelBy,P.TotalAmount,P.Credit,P.MissionCode,P.Distance,P.PlateNumber, DAY(CONVERT(DATE, P.CreatedOn)) AS PlanDate,DAY(ToDate) AS ToDate, MONTH(CONVERT(DATE, P.CreatedOn)) AS PlanMonth, dbo.getMonthKH(ToDate) AS TMonthkh, DAY(CONVERT(DATE, P.FromDate)) AS FromDate, dbo.getMonthKH(P.FromDate) AS FMonthKH, YEAR(CONVERT(DATE, P.CreatedOn)) AS Year, dbo.getMonthKH(P.CreatedOn) AS PlanMonthKH from HRMissionPlan P left join HRStaffProfile SP on SP.EmpCode= P.EmpCode left join HRDepartment D on D.Code=SP.DEPT left join HRMissionPlanMem M on M.MissionCode=P.MissionCode Where P.MissionCode= @MissionCode;
